d Hwy 61, a route along the water so scenic, it seemed a Robert Moses inspired PCH right in northern Minnesota. Across from the stood a one level building with large windows, wild gardens and several Adirondack chairs. We arrived at the <a href=\"http://www.sceniccafe.com\">New Scenic Café</a>.\r\n\r\nJazz that I like to call <em>Woody Allen </em>jazz – the kind of sound played at a fabulous cocktail party in a sophisticated city in his films – gently filled the restaurant. I sat next to a window overlooking a succulent garden and Lake Superior. The walls were of pine wainscoting and decorated with a local artist\'s depictions of horses. I sipped vetliner grüner and the meal that proceeded was one of the most splendid I can recall. Pistachio crusted goat cheese salad. Grilled walleye sandwich on crisp slices of homemade cranberry walnut bread. Tuna and avocado wantons with freshly made wasabi. A marzipan tart with chunks of rhubard sided with a local brew.\r\n\r\nEvery course was delicately prepared yet welcoming and unpretentious. Each flavor was simple and fresh, and designed with intention. It was <em>so </em>good that we bought the cookbook right there. Plus, it has a forward written by none other than Garrison Keillor.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://maidstonebuttermilk.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DSC00211edited.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-410\" src=\"http://maidstonebuttermilk.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DSC00211edited-601x450.jpg\" alt=\"DSC00211edited\" width=\"601\" height=\"450\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<em>Our Traditional Go at Album Cover Inspired Photos. #LookFierce</em>\r\n<h4>Ely</h4>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"yj6qo ajU\">\r\n\r\nNature hiking\r\nLIFE MILESTONES\r\nBeautiful canoe ride\r\nWild rice paddies\r\nStars so bright you can see their reflection in the lake.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n• Minnesota traveling Duluth/Ely and our story\r\n○ Minneapolis\r\n§ Modern Times - tattoos\r\n§ Foundry ?\r\n§ Hunt and Gather\r\n§ More foundry on 1st\r\n§ Marvel; awesome other store; TBF -- all one owner\r\n□ Bachelor Farmer: sweet corn, red herring caught in Lake Superior, homemade ginger cookies; heart wallpaper; exposed beam &amp; wainscoting; exposed ducts-- at Marvel delighted in SuperDry seltzer cocktail and smoky …, store with cool poster of Poliça upcoming performance\r\nYankees vs twins\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','In Search of Lake Wobegon: Adventures in Minnesota','','inherit','open','open','','393-revision-v1','','','2015-07-31 08:09:40','2015-07-31 12:09:40','',393,'http://maidstonebuttermilk.com/393-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
